title: Grateful Dead Live at Kiel Auditorium on 1973-10-29
description:
Set 1

Cold Rain & Snow, Beat It On Down The Line, Brown Eyed Women, Mexicali Blues, Don't Ease Me In, Black Throated Wind, Tennessee Jed, The Race is On, Row Jimmy, El Paso, Eyes Of The World-> China Doll, Around & Around

Set 2

Promised Land-> Bertha-> Greatest Story Ever Told, Loser, Big River, Brokedown Palace, Truckin'-> The Other One-> Wharf Rat-> Sugar Magnolia, E: Casey Jones

reviews.review_text: Fantabulous! Socked in by "Frankenstorm 2012" it is a nice treat to find a '73 audience recording that I do not have. You've turned my cabin fever into a little slice of heaven! Quite a bit of static, unfortunately, but it goes well with the freight train sound of wind outside.
